      <section eId="sec_27_1513">
        <num>27-1513</num>
        <heading>Requirements for regulated medical waste treatment, storage and disposal facility</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_27_1513__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>proof of liability insurance or other form of financial security\ndeemed sufficient by the commissioner to meet all responsibilities in\ncase of release of such waste causing damage; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_27_1513__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>certification that such activities conform with existing local\nzoning laws or ordinances.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
